      <div class="history-item-text">
        The main sources of employment for local residents nowadays are in
        Office Work, Education and the Health Services. Trades and Construction,
        Agriculture, Transport and Retail Sectors also provide a signficant
        number of jobs for local people. Residents' 'travel-to-work' patterns
        show that the main locations for work are in Kirriemuir, Forfar and
        Dundee. There are a few jobs in Westmuir itself - Agriculture,
        Horticulture, Retail and Self-employment of various kinds.
      </div>
    </div>

