      <div class="history-item-text">
        The most recent historical development was the formation of a Community
        Development Group of which all villagers can become members. This new
        initiative has resulted in the creation of a
        <a href="Woodland_Park.html">Community Woodland</a> and recreational
        area in a previously unused area beside Westmuir. This aims to provide a
        designated safe play area for children and to foster an interest in, and
        care of, wildlife in the local environment.
      </div>
    </div>

